  'A high-efficiency Jeju full-island route for travelers with limited time, linking Hallasan, the south coast, and Seongsan Ilchulbong in one day.',
  'Jeju Hallasan, Daepo Jusangjeolli Cliff, Jeongbang Waterfall & Seongsan Ilchulbong Small Group Day Tour | AtoC Korea',
  'Designed for travelers who want to cover Jeju’s core highlights efficiently in one day. From Hallasan and Daepo Jusangjeolli Cliff to Jeongbang Waterfall and Seongsan Ilchulbong, this fast-paced small group tour connects Jeju’s most iconic natural landmarks in a single day.',
